    <bpmn:serviceTask id="Activity_13jsnui" name="Upsert Document" zeebe:modelerTemplate="io.camunda.connector.couchbase.v1" zeebe:modelerTemplateVersion="1" zeebe:modelerTemplateIcon="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
      <bpmn:extensionElements>
        <zeebe:taskDefinition type="io.camunda:couchbase:1" retries="3" />
        <zeebe:taskHeaders>
          <zeebe:header key="operation" value="upsertDocument" />
          <zeebe:header key="elementTemplateVersion" value="1" />
          <zeebe:header key="elementTemplateId" value="io.camunda.connector.couchbase.v1" />
          <zeebe:header key="resultVariable" value="upsert" />
          <zeebe:header key="retryBackoff" value="PT0S" />
        </zeebe:taskHeaders>
        <zeebe:ioMapping>
          <zeebe:input source="couchbase://host.minikube.internal" target="authentication.connectionString" />
          <zeebe:input source="Administrator" target="authentication.username" />
          <zeebe:input source="Password123!" target="authentication.password" />
          <zeebe:input source="demo" target="bucketName" />
          <zeebe:input source="_default" target="scopeName" />
          <zeebe:input source="orders" target="collectionName" />
          <zeebe:input source="=order_id" target="documentId" />
